videos.description: Drew Eubanks throws it down after the adjustment in mid-air on the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Eubanks finishes after tough alley-oop

videos.description: Brandon Randolph rises up and finishes with a flush after picking up the steal on the defensive end.
videos.headline: Randolph gets the steal and slam for Arizona

videos.description: Ira Lee runs the floor and gets rewarded with a huge dunk for Arizona.
videos.headline: Lee throws down big slam in transition

videos.description: Allonzo Trier gets open in transition and knocks down the 3-pointer as Arizona trails Oregon State.
videos.headline: Trier finds the bottom of the net from deep

videos.description: Allonzo Trier puts a defender on a poster after a huge slam.
videos.headline: Trier makes defender regret jumping

videos.description: Rawle Alkins takes off and throws down the two-handed jam in transition.
videos.headline: Alkins shows off in the open floor after the steal

videos.description: Deandre Ayton shows off and makes the dunk in transition look easy.
videos.headline: Ayton flies through the air for the slam

videos.description: Deandre Ayton posts a double-double and Alonzo Trier drops 21 points in Arizona's 62-53 win over Oregon State.
videos.headline: Trier, Ayton fuel Wildcats
